casebody.data:
Cynthia Estelle BOOKER-DOUGLAS, Administratrix of the Estate of Leroy Douglas, Jr., Deceased Employee
v.
J & S TRUCK SERVICE, INC., Employer, Liberty Mutual Insurance Company, Carrier. No. 375P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 5, 2006. Kathleen G. Sumner, Greensboro, for Booker-Douglas. Tonya D. Davis, Jeffrey A. Doyle, Raleigh, for Truck Service, et al.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the conditional petition filed on the 31st day of July 2006 by Defendants in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th day of October 2006."
